        "gg1_-m-5bft_text": "<span style=\"color:#B76C45;font-size:48px;\">Protection</span><span style=\"font-size:48px;\"> Is Not The</span><br><span style=\"font-size:48px;\">Same </span><span style=\"color:#B76C45;font-size:48px;\">As Support</span>",
        "ggzMZ5p1nG1_text": "<p>Most night guards sit between your teeth and absorb pressure.<br>They act as a barrier. Reviv is designed to support the jaw structurally while you sleep.</p>",
        "ggce13CIBBj_text": "Traditional Mouth Guard:",
        "ggoTcCgaFwz_childItem_0": "<p>Blocks enamel damage.</p>",
        "ggoTcCgaFwz_childItem_1": "<p>Sits passively between teeth.</p>",
        "ggoTcCgaFwz_childItem_2": "<p>Focuses on protection only.</p>",
        "gg3l9mc6dLm_text": "Reviv:",
