        "checksum": "594df17b717ceb6819ac7a21e314d78f770d4d8001207d33b587eb0d7095c747_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg22-8NFGtV_text": "<span style=\"color:#4C4E57;font-size:48px;\">What </span><span style=\"color:#B76C45;font-size:48px;\">Structural Support </span><span style=\"color:#4C4E57;font-size:48px;\">Means</span>",
        "ggcgA_PjwuZ_text": "<p>Teeth grinding can be influenced by mechanical stress in the jaw. When the jaw is under tension during sleep, muscles may stay activated, and clenching can continue.</p>",
        "ggAxMQGNdoV_text": "<p>Reviv is engineered to support jaw balance overnight and help reduce excess tension.</p>",
        "ggeVAJP_lTk_childItem_0": "<p>Designed for less mechanical strain.</p>",
        "ggeVAJP_lTk_childItem_1": "<p>Designed to support reduced pressure.</p>",
        "ggeVAJP_lTk_childItem_2": "<p>Simple structural support while you sleep.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_610166881323582246": {
      "type": "gp-section-610166881323582246",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "7614b1903e295416ecc3ddabb3a5cc53d5bf6edef7ca90c22907cff3ce9ce849_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggnBm-lLAI9_text": "<span style=\"color:#4C4E57;\">Why People</span> <span style=\"color:#B76C45;\">Trust Reviv</span>",
        "ggGJtDiLSQD_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/Abdullah_Khalid.png",
        "ggrutWAgWnW_text": "<p>They mocked it. Scoffed at it. REVIV? Just another gimmick. The nights I couldn’t sleep, jaw clenched from the weight of it all. But REVIV was different. It didn’t just straighten my smile, It rebuilt my discipline. You either chew through the pain… Or you stay stuck in it. I chose REVIV.</p>",
        "gg3kuAogyUj_text": "<p>— Abdullah</p>",
        "ggbsF7Ch6Rf_text": "<p>Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggYNu0V9CMt_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/Jason_P.png",
        "gga_NSS4RQL_text": "<p>I’ve tried two different night guards from my dentist and they helped protect my teeth, but I was still clenching all night. With Reviv I became aware of the clenching almost immediately. It feels different. My jaw doesn’t lock down the same way. I still catch myself clenching sometimes, but it’s not constant like before.</p>",
        "ggAGsvPh_74_text": "<p>— Jason</p>",
        "gg3mRmDF-MX_text": "<p>Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggumS_She0t_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0706/4243/4289/files/Tiara_C.png",
        "ggjR-VGzu0D_text": "<p>I wore a custom night guard for years. It stopped the damage, but it never stopped the clenching. It didn’t feel like I was just blocking the grind. It felt like my jaw wasn’t fighting itself anymore. It’s not magic, but it’s the first time I’ve felt actual relief instead of just protection.</p>",
        "ggWN_i4ecxq_text": "<p>— Tiara</p>",
        "gg3lvMqexiU_text": "<p>Verified Customer</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_610167590228067227": {
      "type": "gp-section-610167590228067227",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "05b23ccd582d523b8fe138e50f8469f2bbff6df52555080ab9210f7e8b35a3b7_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg1b9g4nuPZ_text": "Designed For Nightly <span style=\"color:#B76C45;\">Structural Support</span>",
        "ggdX4C6WQtP_text": "<p>Reviv is not just a protective layer. It is built to support your jaw positioning while you sleep.</p>",
        "ggzAPf9Hdg__text": "<p>Reviv R3</p>",
        "ggVg_d20c8L_text": "<p>Advanced Support</p>",
        "ggTUiCwm_PM_childItem_0": "<p>Custom molded for your bite</p>",
        "ggTUiCwm_PM_childItem_1": "<p>Comfortable for overnight wear</p>",
        "ggTUiCwm_PM_childItem_2": "<p>Durable material built for long term use</p>",
        "ggTUiCwm_PM_childItem_3": "<p>Designed around jaw mechanics</p>",
        "ggZN6Qbdr_x_label": "<p>Support Your Structure</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_610169505800258263": {
      "type": "gp-section-610169505800258263",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9b9bd60ce00b170c316cd65bb42503b73834ecdb2153bb01c910805ff2ecf3dd_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg5KxlZL4_M_text": "<span style=\"color:#4C4E57;\">Why People</span> <span style=\"color:#B76C45;\">Trust Reviv</span>",
        "ggUqWRqUEIz_childItem_0": "<p>Why do I keep clenching my jaw even with a traditional night guard?</p>",
        "ggUqWRqUEIz_childItem_1": "<p>How is Reviv different from a standard mouthguard?</p>",
        "ggUqWRqUEIz_childItem_2": "<p>Can orthodontics increase jaw tension or clenching?</p>",
        "ggUqWRqUEIz_childItem_3": "<p>Is jaw clenching just stress?</p>",
        "ggUqWRqUEIz_childItem_4": "<p><strong>Why do I wake up with neck and shoulder tension if the issue is in my jaw?</strong></p>",
        "ggUqWRqUEIz_childItem_5": "<p><strong>Can Reviv change how clenching feels?</strong></p>",
        "ggUqWRqUEIz_childItem_6": "<p><strong>Why would someone choose Reviv instead of more orthodontic work?</strong></p>",
        "ggDRC5Qwcg9_text": "<p>Most night guards are designed to protect your teeth, not address why you’re clenching. If the jaw position feels unstable or compressed, the body may continue activating the jaw muscles at night. Protection is not the same as structural support.</p>",
        "ggvsyGqkqA1_text": "<p>Traditional guards create a barrier between teeth. Reviv is designed to support jaw positioning and help reduce compressive tension. The goal isn’t just to block grinding, but to change the conditions that trigger it.</p>",
        "ggEKXEHHxe0_text": "<p>Some people report increased jaw tightness after extractions, fixed retainers, or aggressive orthodontic movement. If the dental arch is restricted, the jaw may compensate with muscular tension. Reviv focuses on reducing that tension rather than locking teeth into a fixed position.</p>",
        "ggchh1z1UCc_text": "<p>Stress can contribute, but many people clench even when they don’t feel mentally stressed. Structural compression or unstable bite patterns may also contribute to subconscious clenching.</p>",
        "ggt7m802Zaf_text": "<p>The jaw, neck, and upper body are closely connected. Chronic clenching can increase tension through the upper body. Some users report relief in surrounding areas once jaw tension decreases.</p>",
        "ggBcwzdnziq_text": "<p>Some users report becoming more aware of clenching when wearing it. Others notice gradual changes over weeks. The experience varies, and adaptation is part of the process.</p>",
        "gg1s4qX_1x2_text": "<p>Orthodontics focuses on moving teeth into position. Reviv focuses on supporting jaw balance and reducing excess tension. For people whose clenching is driven by tension rather than misalignment alone, addressing the structure may change the pattern of clenching more effectively than simply repositioning teeth.</p>"
      }
    },
